title: McCLOUD 103 Murder Arena [retr?tv]
description:
McCLOUD 103 Murder Arena part 1-2
Stars: Dennis Weaver as McCloud

Part 1: The Concrete Corral   (9/30/1970)  
McCloud is assigned to keep an eye on a boisterous bunch of rodeo riders at Madison Square Garden. While there McCloud encounters more then old friends, an ex-girlfriend and murder.
Guest star: Albert Salmi (Goose Jenkins), Joanna Moore (Donna Roberts), Tom Castronova (Officer), Dennis Fimple (Frankie), Nancy Malone (Iris McKensie), Burr DeBenning (Blue Roberts), James Wainwright (Billy Gibson), Bill McKinney (Reuben)

Part 2: Walk in the Dark  (10/14/1970)   
McCloud complains about his assignment to rodeo detail, so Chief Clifford sends him to Special Auxiliary Force VI under the command of Sgt. Dameron, where he works to catch a murderer in Central Park.
Guest star: Susan Saint James (Officer Keach), Ann Prentiss (Officer Murdock), Stewart Bradley (Lloyd), Lou Massad (Richie), Bart Burns (Reimer), Carol Locatell (Receptionist), Billy Beck (News Vendor), Barbara Gates (Secretary), Albert Salmi (Goose Jenkins), Ken Scott (Det. Vince Polk)
